<ul id="tab">
<li class="active">
<h4>guidelines</h4>
<p><center><h3>the writer&nbsp;&nbsp;</h3></center>

<p>hello lovies! most everyone calls me <b>KC</b>. 30+/f/pst
<p>while i don't have a full time job i make it a point not to spend every waking hour on tumblr. i'm here as much as i feel like i can. and when i'm not you can always find me lurking on discord.
<p>
<br />
<p><center><h3>disclaimer&nbsp;&nbsp;</h3></center>

<p>(1) this blog was created for roleplaying purposes. i am not talia al ghul, magnus bane, eames, tony stark, or their associated actors and i have nothing to do with the properties that they can be found in.
<p>(2) all icons that look like rounded squares, rectangles with symbols or cut off corners or are vertical were created by me with screencaps that i made and i ask that you do not steal them.
<p>
<br />
<p><center><h3>if nothing else read this&nbsp;&nbsp;</h3></center>

<p>(1) the portrayals found on this blog are ones i've worked a long time on. i will <b>NOT</b> change my interpretation of my muses in ways that detract from their core foundations. my muses are my own entity. if i start noticing that you’re ignoring parts of my characters because you don’t like it/don’t agree with it, i reserve the right to drop all threads without warning.
<p>(2) start drama with me about my friends? block me now - because we’re done.
<p>(3) i unfollow for the following:<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#9642; inactive for thirty (30) days or more<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#9642; too much ooc content<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#9642; too much political content<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#9642; posting of drama<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &#9642; too much negativity
<p>
<br />
<p><center><h3>about&nbsp;&nbsp;</h3></center>

<p>(1) most of the muses on this blog are <b>canon divergent</b> &amp; heavily headcanon influenced. please read their biographies and verses before approaching.
<p>(2) this blog is <b>queue</b> heavy.  what that means is all of the replies will be put into a queue that will a certain amount of replies every other day depending on my draft count. this is for my sanity and to keep the dash from being flooded with replies. don’t hesitate to send me an ask if you want to know when your reply will be posted.
<p>(3) this blog has a <b>weekend rule</b>. what that means is each saturday and sunday will be spent away from tumblr completely. no replies, no follow backs, no asks, no nothing on tumblr will be done until the following monday.
<p>(4) the queue is tagged for your blacklisting purposes.
<p>(5) this blog is <b>highly selective</b>. what that means is i will carefully look over a blog to see whether or not i can see myself writing with them. i also look to see if our writing could be compatible. this blog is also <b>mutuals</b> only. meaning if i follow you and you follow me. all starter calls are for <b>mutuals only</b>. please double check to see if we are following each other before or liking a starter call. <b>memes</b> are open to <b>non-mutuals</b> unless otherwise tagged.
<p>(6) i do not follow for follow. if we write together continuously, or we have plotted something out long term I have no problem hitting the follow button. otherwise i prefer to keep a relatively clean dash. this is nothing against you. this is for myself and my dash.
<p>(7) when it comes to unfollowing it is usually done for the following reasons: inactive for thirty (30) days or more, too much ooc content, posting of drama, or too much negativity. i’m here to write, have fun, and forget about the real world for just a little bit. if you decide to return to your inactive blog and we were mutuals feel free to hit me up and i’ll refollow. otherwise i figure you have decided to move on from that blog and see no point in following an inactive one.
<p>(8) i will also unfollow anyone who decides to attack, harass, or do anything similar to those i consider my friends. in my opinion if you go after someone i call friend you are going after me and i will not tolerate that no matter what.
<p>(9) please do not contact me and ask why i unfollowed you. any and all such asks will be deleted as they are covered in the rules. harassing me in such a matter will only lead me to block you instead of just unfollowing you.
<p>(10) do not god-mod my character. if i catch you doing so without my permission consider the thread dropped.
<p>(11) this is a hate free blog. any hate received will be deleted on sight. if i find those i follow sending hate i will unfollow you in a heartbeat. remember to treat others as you would like to be treated in return.
<p>(12) with this blog i prefer to roleplay multi-para to novella. while i can write one liners i feel like there is no character development to those threads and can be easily dropped. multi-para to me is a minimum of three paragraphs, while novella is anywhere over 1k words.
<p>(13) please <b>do not reblog</b> threads unless you are a participant in them. feel free to like them all you want but unless you and i are writing together i ask that you don’t reblog them as it makes it difficult to keep up with whose turn it is in the thread.
<p>(14) please <b>make a new post</b> if you want to continue asks. i am all for continuing asks but i will not respond to any that have not been moved into a new post.
<p>(15) when it comes to memes <b>please specify a muse</b>. if you don't specify any muse your ask will be deleted no questions asked. i'm not a mind reader and i'm not going to throw a muse at you that you may be uncomfortable with.

<p>
<br />
<p><center><h3>the mun&nbsp;&nbsp;</h3></center>

<p>(1) the mun has a life outside of tumblr and asks that everyone please be patient. any and all replies that are seen will be replied to. if for some reason a reply has been missed a gentle reminder in the ask box is appreciated. but please do not constantly harass the mun for a reply.
<p>(2) the mun is of age (21+) which means there will be nsfw elements on this blog. that could mean violence, torture, gore, and scenes of a sexual nature. we will <b>not</b> write sexual scenes with those who are under 18. there is the option of fade to black or the morning after for those who are not of age
<p>(3) all nsfw posts will be tagged <b>not safe for the city</b> for your blacklisting purposes.

<p>
<br />
<p><center><h3>relationships&nbsp;&nbsp;</h3></center>

<p>(1) this is a multi-ship, multi-verse blog. i ship chemistry first and foremost. if there is chemistry a relationship is possible. please read the muses biographies and verses to get an idea as to what sorts of relationships they are open to.
<p>(2) when it comes to relationships my muses span the spectrum to be outlined on their respective biographies. relationships with these muses will not be easy but if you're willing to put in the work they will be worth it
<p>(3) <b>IF YOU WRITE A CANON ROMANTIC PARTNER:</b> while i do acknowledge those relationships as canon i will not roleplay it instantly. i would prefer that we have written together to make certain that our writing styles are compatible. after that i ask that we have at least spoken out of character first. while it isn’t necessary it helps to have that communication out of character.
<p>(4) please do not force a ship on me. nor try to engage us in instant ships. i prefer all ships to be written out and developed over time. forced shipping, instant ships, etc. are the fastest way to send us both running in the opposite direction.
<p>(5) there is more to my muses than their fcs. if you are here to do nothing more than to get into bed with them i ask that you do not follow. i am not here to write purely smut. I prefer to write threads with plots and if smut happens, it happens as part of the thread.

<p>
<br />
<p><center><h3>exclusivity&nbsp;&nbsp;</h3></center>

<p>(1) at this time this blog is exclusive to a select group of muses. those that are exclusive to this blog as a whole are listed on the <b>pan-blog exclusives</b> tab. there are <b>two</b> exceptions to the pan-blog exclusives and that is sophie moore &amp; jacob kane. <b>affcgato</b> is our main kate kane but she is not exclusive to sophie moore nor jacob kane. those that are exclusive to a certain muse can be found on that muse's popup.
<p>(2) what this means is i will not write with any other version of the muses listed under exclusive. it has nothing to do with you and your muse. there is a connection between their muse and my own that i feel can't be replicated.
<p>(3) the exclusivity can and will change if muses go inactive or delete. also, being exclusive means we've talked a great deal ooc and have plotted things out between our muses. while i would prefer it to be mutual i will not demand it.

<p>
<br />
<p><center><h3>ocs &amp; children&nbsp;&nbsp;</h3></center>

<p>(1) this blog is oc friendly but selective due to past problems. i will give your muse a chance but if i feel like our writing styles are incompatible i will drop the thread
<p>(2) in regards to children, all muses will not acknowledge any original characters that claim them as the parent. please don’t take this personally as this is nothing against you, the mun, but a personal preference of mine. canon children associated with each muse, on the other hand, will be acknowledged.

<p>
<br />
<p><center><h3>misc&nbsp;&nbsp;</h3></center>

<p>(1) i reserve the right to add to these rules as i see fit.

</li>

