<center><h3>loki laufeyson</h3></center>
<p>
<div id="verse">
<div id="right"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/k3nvVov.png"></div>
<a href="#?w=530" rel="03" class="poplight" title="muse &amp; verse info"><b>loki</b></a> &mdash; <i>mcu canon based, divergent timeline as seen in endgame</i>. loki is the biological son of laufey, the ruler of the frost giants in jotunheim, who was abandoned and left to die shortly after his birth. found by odin, loki was taken to asgard and raised by him and frigga as an asgardian prince, along with thor. following the battle of new york loki was given an opportunity he couldn't pass up; a chance to free himself with the tesseract. this is the loki that now exists as the other version of himself was killed by thanos. 
<p><b>faceclaim:</b> tom hiddleston
