<h4>harry potter</h4>
<br />
<center><h3>lanie blackstone</h3></center>
<p>
<div id="verse">
<div id="left"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/GMgTTGw.png"></div>
<a href="#?w=530" rel="11" class="poplight" title="muse &amp; verse info"><b>lanie</b></a> &mdash; <i>original character, canon based, compliant with all hp books & movies</i>. born into an old, pureblood family, lanie was the first to ever be sorted into hufflepuff. she was also the first to spend most of her life living in the muggle world. currently a hit wizard with the department of magical law enforcement, she splits her time between her flat in london and the family home in the english countryside. 
<p><b>faceclaim:</b> alexandra daddario
</div>
<br />
<p>
<center><h3>west morgan</h3></center>
<p>
<div id="verse">
<div id="right"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/RWHR59U.png"></div>
<a href="#?w=530" rel="12" class="poplight" title="muse &amp; verse info"><b>west</b></a> &mdash; <i>original character, canon based, compliant with all hp books & movies</i>. an american half-blood currently living in london and working as the head of the spell damaged department at saint mungos. west moved to london after a tragedy forced him to look for a new place to start all over again. he tends to be quiet and dedicated to his work but he's also loyal to those around him. 
<p><b>faceclaim:</b> gareth david-lloyd
</div>
