<a href="#?w=530" rel="13" class="poplight" title="muse &amp; verse info"><b>david arkwright</b></a> &mdash; <i>original character, canon based, compliant with all hp books & movies</i>. an english pureblood wizard, current defence against the dark arts professor at hogwarts, and splitting his time between the castle and his small flat in london. a former death eater, he promised the headmistress that he was reformed and no longer believed in those ideals. unfortunately, he not only belives in them, but has an even darker secret that no one knows.
<p><b>faceclaim:</b> jonathan rhys meyers 
</div>
