<a href="#?w=530" rel="14" class="poplight" title="muse &amp; verse info"><b>mangus bane</b></a> &mdash; <i>show based blended canon with book influence</i>. magnus bane is the current high warlock of brooklyn and involved with alec lightwood, of the new york institute. being over four centuries old, his life has since intertwined with several shadowhunters and downworlders over the centuries. notable relationships include camille belcourt, imasu morales, dorthea rollins, & george. catarina loss, ragnor fell, raphael santiago, simon lewis, luke garroway & henry branwell are considered some of his friends. 
