<li>
<h4>inception</h4>
<br />
<center><h3>jamison eames</h3></center>
<p>
<div id="verse">
<div id="left"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/EXcJQFE.png"></div>
<a href="#?w=530" rel="17" class="poplight" title="muse &amp; verse info"><b>eames</b></a> &mdash; <i>canon & headcanon based</i>. eames is an essential part of the secrecy and deceit within the dream world. he can project the image of anyone, essentially forging an identity as a literal physical manifestation. combined with his ability to mirror other people's mannerisms and behaviors, he is a very capable doppelganger. this skill comes in handy, and can help convince another person that whomever team needs him to be in order to aid their deception. he frequently uses a heckler and koch p2000 throughout the first level defending the taxi and city warehouse from projections, a south african mgl grenade launcher and a sig sg 552 assault rifle with custom arctic camouflage while planting charges in the hospital. he is also seen holding a beretta 92fs inox. his totem is a poker chip. 
<p><b>faceclaim:</b> tom hardy
</div>
<br />
<p>
<center><h3>zane lennon</h3></center>
<p>
<div id="verse">
<div id="right"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/gI7vymE.png"></div>
<a href="#?w=530" rel="18" class="poplight" title="muse &amp; verse info"><b>zane</b></a> &mdash; <i>original character</i>. boredom always led to trouble. more so than not when it came to zane. his life of crime started early, during his school days in london, england. whenever someone wanted a forged id he was the one to talk to. that path led him into crime in the real world, working with a partner and learning about the sorts of things his talents could really do. never did he expect to find dreamsharing and now that he's been exposed he knows he'll never find anything that beats it.
<p><b>faceclaim:</b> logan marshall-green
</div>
<br />
<p>
<center><h3>finley langston</h3></center>
<p>
<div id="verse">
<div id="left"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/9KqSkZD.png"></div>
<a href="#?w=530" rel="19" class="poplight" title="muse &amp; verse info"><b>finley</b></a> &mdash; <i>original character</i>. cia interrogator finley langston is the last person you expect to find in dreamsharing. as a government official, she normally is the sort who would be against using dreamsharing. but being exposed to it in college she knew just how much of an asset it could be. even more so when it came to interrogating prisoners in the aftermath of 9/11.
<p><b>faceclaim:</b> jessica chastain 
</div>
<br />
<p>
</li>

