<a href="#?w=530" rel="20" class="poplight" title="muse &amp; verse info"><b>yennefer</b></a> &mdash; <i>canon based on the netflix series</i>. yennefer was a sorceress from vengerberg, the capital city of aedirn, before being recruited by tissaia de vries and brought to aretuza to study magic. in time she meets geralt of rivia and while the two form an uneasy partnership, she knows her feelings for him complicate matters. especially given the circumstances on how they met. 
<p><b>faceclaim:</b> anya chalotra
</div>
