<a href="https://ofangelicblood.tumblr.com"><b>ofangelicblood</b></a> &mdash; show based, book influenced jace herondale of the mortal instruments series. private &amp; highly selective. while this blog still pulls heavily from the freeform series, elements of the books are slowly being added to the blended canon main verse. for those who prefer the show there are arcs that follow each series. and for those who prefer the books there is a <b>request only</b> book verse along with arcs for each book. <br />
<br />
we can be found on this blog <b>tue</b>
