<h4>non rp blogs</h4>
<div id="verse">
<div id="left"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/5oHcfne.png"></div>
<p><b>RP hub</b> || <a href="http://houseofsol.tumblr.com/">@houseofsol</a>. the collective RP hub (sideblog) for all of my blogs. this blog collects all of my resources (banners, writing references, fonts, theme things, aesthetics, etc) all in one place. all of my important ooc updates will be posted here, even if they are not reblogged to other blogs. this is also the central hub for all my themes currently available to the public
<br />
</div>
