<center><h3>main verse</h3></center>
<p>
<div id="verse">
<div id="nleft"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/6e29wMd.png"></div>
<b>never tell me the odds</b> &mdash; <a href="/tagged/⸢ verse → han ⸥ ❛ v; never tell me the odds ❜ || main">threads</a>: movie based verse that covers all the movies from solo through the rise of skywalker. each individual movie has its own arc and threads pertaining to those movies will be placed there.
</div>
<p>
<center><h3>reincarnation</h3></center>
<p>
<div id="verse">
<div id="nright"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/6e29wMd.png"></div>
<b>the force seemingly has a sense of humour</b> &mdash; <a href="/tagged/⸢ verse → han ⸥ ❛ v; the force seemingly has a sense of humour ❜ || alternate">threads</a>: his death on the starkiller at the hands of his son was supposed to be permanent. the force seemed to have other ideas. after throwing him back into life as his younger self, he knows this is a rare second chance at life and one he's not going to throw away.
</div>
<p>
<center><h3>modern</h3></center>
<p>
<div id="verse">
<div id="nleft"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/6e29wMd.png"></div>
<b>nothing is impossible</b> &mdash; <a href="/tagged/⸢ verse → han ⸥ ❛ v; nothing is impossible ❜ || alternate">threads</a>: han is a former air force pilot turned into government double agent/smuggler. even though he's married to united states senator leia organa, he rarely sees her or their son, ben. it's part of the job and it's meant to keep them safe. until one day the job decides it's had enough of him in it.
</div>
<p>
<center><h3>pacific rim</h3></center>
<p>
<div id="verse">
<div id="nright"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/6e29wMd.png"></div>
<b>a man's gotta do what a man's gotta do</b> &mdash; <a href="/tagged/⸢ verse → han ⸥ ❛ v; a man’s gotta do what a man’s gotta do ❜ || pacific rim">threads</a> alternate verse: a former military pilot who ended up being too old for the jaeger program even with all of his experience. he turned to smuggling goods to those who were willing to pay and those who wanted them. not only to make a living, but also to put a lot of the skills he learned as a pilot to use. though once the attacks become more frequent he has to get creative with how he smuggles things into and out of the cities where he lives. once he ends up in hong kong he finds himself also helping the orphans in the city find new homes.
</div>
