<h4>verses</h4>
<br />
<center><h3>main verse</h3></center>
<p>
<div id="verse">
<div id="nleft"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/Y2O285Z.png"></div>
<b>hopping in an x wing to blow shit up</b> &mdash; <a href="/tagged/⸢ verse → poe ⸥ ❛ v; hopping in an x wing to blow shit up ❜ || main">threads</a> main verse: movie based verse that covers all the movies from the force awakens through the rise of skywalker. each individual movie has its own arc and threads pertaining to those movies will be placed there.
</div>
<p>
<center><h3>pacific rim</h3></center>
<p>
<div id="verse">
<div id="nright"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/Y2O285Z.png"></div>
<b>fortune favours the brave</b> &mdash; <a href="/tagged/⸢ verse → poe ⸥ ❛ v; fortune favours the brave ❜ || pacific rim">threads</a> alternate verse: he’d always known his place would be inside the cockpit of a jaeger. poe had worked hard to be good and while it was also reckless it tended to come out in their favour. until an accident caused the death of his drift partner and he was left without anyone willing to copilot. not wanting his skills to go to waste the defense corp recruited him to work with pilots and to hopefully find a new drift partner that he might be able to work with so he can help them fight their war against the kaiju.
</div>
