<center><h3>trivia</h3></center>
<p>&#9642; leto manages to survive the poison that his traitorous doctor gave him, slipping out of the palace once those from house harkonnen gather their dead.
<p>&#9642; he was assumed to have died from the poison since no one saw him flee into the desert. changing his name, he lives in secrecy with the freman and does his best to avoid crossing paths with paul and lady jessica.
