<b>there is no call we do not answer</b> &mdash; <a href="/tagged/⸢ verse → leto ⸥ ❛ v; there is no call we do not answer ❜ || main">threads</a>:  this verse is based in and around the 2021 movie. it will explore leto's life on caladan as well as the short amount of time he spent on arrakis. after the attack, he manages to survive the poisoning and joins the freman in the desert. not wanting to draw attention to himself, he changes his name and tries to avoid crossing paths with lady jessican and paul. 
